{"tid":1967631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"繼美國加拿大後，英國傾倒牛奶150万升每天，價格跌到5便士每升","createTime":"2020-04-11T05:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T06:18:50.000Z","uid":353114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f27a2157f4fd6719803ce5bd04f22841f3555f78","tid":1967631,"uid":353114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"因為大量過剩，牛奶價格已經跌到底。在一家市場裏，原本牛奶大概25便士-30便士/L<br />\n上週末，這個價格跌到了7便士，到週二，價格又跌到5便士&ldquo;考慮到還有運輸成本大概要2-3便士，這牛奶幾乎就是白送了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n英國180萬頭奶牛還在源源不斷的下奶，陽光越好，奶牛產的奶越多<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但麻煩的是，我們不能讓員工回家休息，農場還得繼續，我們還要繼續照顧奶牛，繼續給它們擠奶。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n同時，有地方反而限購每人4樽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWYaiKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWYaiKM.jpg&h=6b19758f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHneLpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHneLpN.jpg&h=c3d42a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAeMBws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAeMBws.jpg&h=f39c865d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zET0X8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zET0X8.jpg&h=f099220d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY7uziG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY7uziG.gif&h=61c50c75&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUHm9R2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUHm9R2.gif&h=3048152a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCxKob2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCxKob2.jpg&h=fd283186&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P55G9R3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP55G9R3.gif&h=b1c879d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZgTxw4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://